  "content": [
    {
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "chapterTitle": "04 大脑预防疲劳比患者本身更有先见之明",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "25178841_9_5650-5757",
          "range": "5650-5757",
          "rangeStart": 5650,
          "rangeEnd": 5757,
          "markText": "人体不是直接对肌肉疲劳做出反应，而是大脑在达到极限前做出反应：让人感觉疲劳，在发生损伤征象前停止运动。换句话说，疲劳不是生理事件，而是一种感觉，通过大脑来阻止灾难性伤害的发生。他们称之为“执行中枢控制的大脑系统”。",
          "colorStyle": 0,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1721783006,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-07-24 09:03:26",
          "chapterUid": 9,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25178841&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=5650&rangeEnd=5757",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f7a32b70718032d9f7a4c60?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=5650&rangeEnd=5757"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "bookReviews": [],
  "hotBookmarks": [
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25178841_3_2030-2053",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "2030-2053",
      "markText": "医者，看的是病，开的是药，救的是心，给的是情。",
      "totalCount": 612,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25178841&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=2030&rangeEnd=2053",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f7a32b70718032d9f7a4c60?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=2030&rangeEnd=2053"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25178841_3_2536-2572",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "2536-2572",
      "markText": "非传染性疾病的根源是不健康的生活方式，医生只能治标，治本还要靠患者自己。",
      "totalCount": 221,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25178841&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=2536&rangeEnd=2572",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f7a32b70718032d9f7a4c60?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=2536&rangeEnd=2572"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25178841_4_4517-4583",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "4517-4583",
      "markText": "疾病已不再由患者的主观体验决定，而是由其身体的健康状况所定义。因此，如果患者感觉不舒服但医生却看不出问题，医生将会按身体无恙来处理。",
      "totalCount": 162,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25178841&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=4517&rangeEnd=4583",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f7a32b70718032d9f7a4c60?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=4517&rangeEnd=4583"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25178841_3_1809-1858",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "1809-1858",
      "markText": "类似的案例不胜枚举，在每天就诊的患者中，有1/3的病因不在心脏，而是精神或心理问题导致的胸背部不适",
      "totalCount": 150,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25178841&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1809&rangeEnd=1858",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f7a32b70718032d9f7a4c60?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1809&rangeEnd=1858"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25178841_3_736-770",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "736-770",
      "markText": "人类机体的自愈能力，如免疫功能、自我修复功能、再生功能和代偿功能等。",
      "totalCount": 128,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25178841&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=736&rangeEnd=770",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f7a32b70718032d9f7a4c60?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=736&rangeEnd=770"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25178841_7_5640-5671",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "5640-5671",
      "markText": "患者以不同的方式去理解它们，他们的症状就会产生相应不同的变化。",
      "totalCount": 128,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25178841&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=5640&rangeEnd=5671",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f7a32b70718032d9f7a4c60?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=5640&rangeEnd=5671"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25178841_9_6133-6204",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "6133-6204",
      "markText": "热天行动迟缓，不是源于肌肉力竭，而是中枢控制系统限制体力活动以免身体过热；生病时，免疫系统的信号诱发疲乏，促使我们休息，节省能量用来抵抗感染。",
      "totalCount": 126,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25178841&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=6133&rangeEnd=6204",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f7a32b70718032d9f7a4c60?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=6133&rangeEnd=6204"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25178841_4_3911-3969",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "3911-3969",
      "markText": "古希腊名医希波克拉底以见证者的身份大谈特谈“人体固有的自愈力”，而2世纪的医生盖仑则认为“自信和信念远比药物有效”。",
      "totalCount": 120,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25178841&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=3911&rangeEnd=3969",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f7a32b70718032d9f7a4c60?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=3911&rangeEnd=3969"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25178841_6_6404-6433",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "6404-6433",
      "markText": "似乎他们相信已经得到了一种有效的治疗，从而使症状得以缓解。",
      "totalCount": 120,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25178841&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=6404&rangeEnd=6433",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f7a32b70718032d9f7a4c60?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=6404&rangeEnd=6433"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25178841_4_4701-4721",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "4701-4721",
      "markText": "不可靠的人类体验被确切的指标数据所取代。",
      "totalCount": 108,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25178841&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=4701&rangeEnd=4721",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f7a32b70718032d9f7a4c60?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=4701&rangeEnd=4721"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25178841_6_4889-4943",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "4889-4943",
      "markText": "椎体成形术治愈了邦妮的脊柱骨折，但是当初参加手术试验时，邦妮自己并不知道，她做的不是椎体成形术，而是假手术。",
      "totalCount": 108,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25178841&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=4889&rangeEnd=4943",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f7a32b70718032d9f7a4c60?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=4889&rangeEnd=4943"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25178841_7_16123-16162",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "16123-16162",
      "markText": "换句话说，不要随意地就把药丸扔到喉咙里。相反，你应该在服用药物时创造一种仪式。",
      "totalCount": 108,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25178841&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=16123&rangeEnd=16162",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f7a32b70718032d9f7a4c60?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=16123&rangeEnd=16162"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25178841_3_1154-1207",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "1154-1207",
      "markText": "医学既需整合，也要个体化；我们既要理性看待科学证据和客观检查结果，也要重视个体情感和心理对躯体造成的影响。",
      "totalCount": 104,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25178841&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1154&rangeEnd=1207",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f7a32b70718032d9f7a4c60?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1154&rangeEnd=1207"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25178841_4_799-867",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "799-867",
      "markText": "顺势疗法实际上是用昂贵瓶子装上水制剂（或糖片）。在治疗中，活性物质通过用水反复稀释和强烈摇动得到的最终药剂，连原始物质的一个分子都没有。",
